{"tid":2249591,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"亞阿再互轟 停火協議閃電摧毀","createTime":"2020-10-19T12:25:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T12:35:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c72e60fc6728057041cf75c09775787dffc3413a","tid":2249591,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T12:25:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201019/PFHUJ643JBA75JCG6WZ5DV7MZA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201019%2FPFHUJ643JBA75JCG6WZ5DV7MZA%2F&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9Zs0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=235de097\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201019%2FPFHUJ643JBA75JCG6WZ5DV7MZA%2F&h=7eeaeb5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201019/PFHUJ643JBA75JCG6WZ5DV7MZA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n亞阿再互轟 停火協議閃電摧毀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ISvpf3XxUDgDSik7bR_6Gz9aWBg=/1342x698/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TIEUQCIYWBFKTEMO6FJBIQ7CWM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FISvpf3XxUDgDSik7bR_6Gz9aWBg%3D%2F1342x698%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTIEUQCIYWBFKTEMO6FJBIQ7CWM.jpg&h=42f11cc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■阿塞拜疆國防部前天發放發動攻擊片段。<br />\n<br />\n衝突不斷的亞美尼亞和阿塞拜疆的第二次人道停火協議，昨日午夜生效，但亞美尼亞指對方在協議生效數分鐘後即發射炮彈和火箭空襲，阿塞拜疆亦指對方向多個地方開火。<br />\n<br />\n阿塞拜疆第二大城市甘賈上周被納卡地區發射導彈空襲，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n由亞美尼亞人控制的納卡地區軍方指停火協議生效後，阿塞拜疆再轟炸其首府斯捷潘奈克特，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n衝突釀700死<br />\n<br />\n兩國對上一周原在俄羅斯斡旋下達成人道停火協議，準備就有主權爭議的納卡地區展開「實質談判」，但旋即互相指控違議。俄羅斯外長拉夫羅夫前晚致電兩國外長，敦促雙方遵守停火協議。<br />\n<br />\n納卡地區在國際法下屬阿塞拜疆，但實質上由亞美尼亞分離分子控制，在蘇聯倒台後曾宣佈獨立但不獲承認。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n法新社/路透社"},{"pid":"e476d4e365f3d59375a2d3f8c9b2c0c099ed7820","tid":2249591,"uid":78873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T12:26:58.000Z","msg":"亞狗 屌你老母停撚咗火都搞9人."},{"pid":"e2cfed50ca1493e45f9b8c534c8280d22ecb7a9e","tid":2249591,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T12:28:37.000Z","msg":"蛾狗收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c83e85bd362e65d9777be6adc11da1ad07ae262","tid":2249591,"uid":254788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T12:33:06.000Z","msg":"冇人聽俄狗講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"100ba90927c7c87df249599a7d3838d74ebdfbe8","tid":2249591,"uid":276548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T12:33:56.000Z","msg":"@(黃)黎(智)子(英)蜂 @爾多奸"},{"pid":"98c826e647eb332bb4d333a1055ad11b281cab11","tid":2249591,"uid":276548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"100ba90927c7c87df249599a7d3838d74ebdfbe8","tid":2249591,"uid":276548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T12:33:56.000Z","msg":"@(黃)黎(智)子(英)蜂 @爾多奸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T12:35:49.000Z","msg":"@黎子蜂 呢頭傻鳩三毛 好鐘意講咩爾多奸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}